data.description:
Stunning 5 Bedroom Home with Bonus Spaces and Lake Access in West Lake Manor**

Welcome to this updated and beautifully maintained 5-bedroom home in the desirable West Lake Manor community. This residence offers a perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionality.

The home boasts five spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or hosting guests. The upstairs bonus room is versatile for use as an extra bedroom, sitting area, gym, or home office. Bonus step-down space is currently used as a man cave but is easily convertible into a kids' playroom.

The home has 2.5 baths downstairs and 1 upstairs. Located in West Lake Manor, residents enjoy lake access and boat slip privileges when HOA dues are paid. 

 Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
